  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink47-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">pāṉaṟku vayil maṟutta talaimakaḷ piṉ appāṇaṉōṭu talaimakaṉ pukuntu taṉ
          kātaṉmai kūṟiyavaḻic colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink47">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>muḷḷeyiṟṟup pāṇmaka ḷiṉkeṭiṟu corinta</l>
          <l>vakaṉperu vaṭṭi niṟaiya maṉaiyō</l>
          <l>ḷarikāṟ perumpayaṟu niṟaikku mūra</l>
          <l>māṇiḻai yāya maṟiyuniṉ</l>
          <l>pāṇaṉ pōlap palapoyt tallē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> O man from the village! </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> Where a wife [takes] big green-gram, its stalks cut off, and fills</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> a big basket until it fills to the brim</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> – [a basket already] emptied of sweet Keṭiṟu fish by the bard's
            daughter, </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> she with teeth like thorns. </l>
          <l> My dazzling jewel-bedecked girlfriends know </l>
          <l> about the many lies you tell – just like your bard! </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
